profile: At Lighthouse, you are our first and only priority. We work with you to make you feel comfortable while educating you about your home. Whether you are buying or selling, we will show you both the positive and negative aspects of the property. We take the time to investigate every nook and cranny and treat your home as if it were our own. We offer Pre-purchase inspections, Pre-sale or pre-listing inspections, Commercial Inspections and Rural Property Inspections.  Our inspectors have full errors and omission insurance coverage.
warranty_terms: We are committed to your satisfaction with our services, to the extend of a full refund of fees paid.
